---
title: Quick Pomegranate-Glazed Fish with Sumac Veggie & Radish Couscous Salad
description: If pomegranate glazed doesn’t quip your interest and get your tastebuds fired up, we don’t want else will. On a fresh white fish it pops out of the bowl. Add the pomegranate fish to a sumac veggie couscous and that’s a done deal. Go on dig in, we know you’re interested now.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
